transcripts: Soniclear is a powerful yet gentle sonic cleansing system designed to elevate skin cleansing to a whole new level. Powered by sonic waves the Soniclear micro massages away dirt, oil, perspiration and makeup and provides gentle exfoliation with brush speeds in excess of 300 times per second it's gentle enough to use up to twice a day for most skin types and conditions there is no more advanced skin cleansing technology than Soniclear.
